---

<section class="py-24 bg-[#fff1f2] text-center">
    <div class="container max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 flex flex-col items-center">
        <h2
            class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-black text-slate-900 mb-6 leading-tight text-center"
        >
            Maximiza el potencial de tu obra con <br />
            <span class="italic font-black">CONKRET</span>
        </h2>
        <p
            class="text-lg text-slate-600 mb-16 max-w-2xl mx-auto font-medium leading-relaxed text-center"
        >
            Soluciones integrales diseñadas para garantizar la eficiencia,
            calidad y seguridad que tu proyecto necesita.
        </p>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
            <!-- Card 1 -->
            <div
                class="feature-card bg-white rounded-[2rem] overflow-hidden shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-2 transition-transform duration-300 reveal-on-scroll opacity-0 translate-y-8"
            >
                <div class="h-64 overflow-hidden relative">
                    <img
                        src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dskliu1ig/image/upload/v1769563933/conkret-peru-concreto-listo_dwaisx.webp"
                        alt="Entrega Puntual"
                        class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-700 hover:scale-110"
                    />
                    <div
                        class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/50 to-transparent"
                    >
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div
                    class="relative bg-white"
                    style="padding: 12px !important;"
                >
                    <h3
                        class="text-2xl font-black text-slate-900 mb-4"
                        style="padding-top: 15px !important; margin-top: 0 !important;"
                    >
                        Entrega Puntual
                    </h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed text-sm">
                        Mixers despachados con GPS para asegurar la llegada
                        exacta a tu obra en todo Lima.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Card 2 -->
            <div
                class="feature-card bg-white rounded-[2rem] overflow-hidden shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-2 transition-transform duration-300 reveal-on-scroll opacity-0 translate-y-8"
                data-delay="200"
            >
                <div class="h-64 overflow-hidden relative">
                    <img
                        src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dskliu1ig/image/upload/v1769562141/1-4-mortero-grueso_odjo1y.webp"
                        alt="Calidad Certificada"
                        class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-700 hover:scale-110"
                    />
                    <div
                        class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/50 to-transparent"
                    >
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div
                    class="relative bg-white"
                    style="padding: 12px !important;"
                >
                    <h3
                        class="text-2xl font-black text-slate-900 mb-4"
                        style="padding-top: 15px !important; margin-top: 0 !important;"
                    >
                        Calidad Certificada
                    </h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed text-sm">
                        Dosificación industrializada por peso que garantiza la
                        resistencia f'c contratada.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Card 3 -->
            <div
                class="feature-card bg-white rounded-[2rem] overflow-hidden shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-2 transition-transform duration-300 reveal-on-scroll opacity-0 translate-y-8"
                data-delay="400"
            >
                <div class="h-64 overflow-hidden relative">
                    <img
                        src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1541888946425-d81bb19240f5?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=800"
                        alt="Asesoría Técnica"
                        class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-700 hover:scale-110"
                    />
                    <div
                        class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/50 to-transparent"
                    >
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div
                    class="relative bg-white"
                    style="padding: 12px !important;"
                >
                    <h3
                        class="text-2xl font-black text-slate-900 mb-4"
                        style="padding-top: 15px !important; margin-top: 0 !important;"
                    >
                        Asesoría Técnica
                    </h3>
                    <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed text-sm">
                        Ingenieros especialistas disponibles para recomendarte
                        la mejor mezcla para tu proyecto.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    /* Additional custom shadows specifically for this clean look if Tailwind's aren't enough */
    .feature-card {
        box-shadow: 0 20px 40px -5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
    }
</style>
